quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,61,"Tuma nde Fir'awna e yimЙ“e mu'un Й“en fewtundirnoo e Muusaa e yimЙ“e mu'un, nokku ka wonnoo fedde kala no yi'ude ndeya, yimЙ“e Muusaa Й“en wi'i: "Pellet, Fir'awna e yimЙ“e mu'un Й“en Й“e hewtitoto en, en alaa dartantooЙ—o en Й“e"."
  26,62,"Muusaa maakani yimЙ“e makko Й“en: "Fiyaake Й—en wanaa no miijorton non. Pellet, Joomi am no wonndiri e am semmbinngol e wallugol, O fewnay lam O tinndina lam faade e laawol daЙ—ugol"."
  26,63,"Men Wahayini e Muusaa ko Men yamiray Й“e mo yo o piyir maayo ngon tuggordu makko ndun, o piyiri ngo ndu, maayo ngon seekii ngo wonti boli sappoo e Й—iЙ—i yeru limoore leЖҙЖҙi Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, kala huntere e ceeki maayo ngon foti e fello mawngo ka tiiЙ—ugol e ka tabitugol haa nokku ka ndiyam ilataa e majje."
  26,64,"Men Й“anni Firawna e yimЙ“e makko Й“en haa Й“e naati ka maayo ko Й“e sikkuЙ“e wonnde laawol ngol ko lummbu ngol."
  26,65,"Men danndi Muusaa e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko immorde e Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en, hay gooto e maЙ“Й“e halkanooka."
  26,66,"Refti Men halkiri Fir'awna e yimЙ“e makko Й“en yooleede ka maayo."
  26,67,"Pellet, no e seekanagol maayo ngon Muusaa e daЙ—ugol makko e halkeede Fir'awana e yimЙ“e makko Й“en Й—um ko Aaya tinndinЙ—o e dow goongugol Muusaa. ЖҒurЙ“e heewude e Й“en wonndunooЙ“e e Fir'awna Й“e wonaano gomЙ—inЙ“e."
  26,68,"Anndu Joomi maaЙ—a -an NulaaЙ—o-ko Kanko woni tedduЙ—o YoЙ“totooЙ—o ayЙ“e Makko Й“en, YurmeteeЙ—o on tuubuЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e."
  26,69,"Janngu e taweede maЙ“Й“e -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee fii Ibraahiima."
  26,70,"Tuma nde o wi'annoo baaba makko Aajara e yimЙ“e mu'un Й“en: "Ko honЙ—um wonuЙ—on rewude gaanin Alla?""
  26,71,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'ani mo: "Ko sanamuuji men rewata, men Гұalla ГұiiЙ“ude e rewugol Й—i, ko men jokkuЙ“e Й—i"."
  26,72,"Ibraahiima maakani Й“e: "Yalli sanamuuji Й—in no nana noddaandu mo'on ndun tuma noddoton Й—i?""
  26,73,"Kaa hiЙ—i nafa on si on Й—oftike Й—i, maaЙ—um Й—i lorra on si on yeddii Й—i?"
  26,74,"ЖҒe wi'i: "ЖҠi nanantaa men dey si men noddii Й—i, Й—i nafataa men kadi si men Й—oftike Й—i, Й—i lorrataa men kadi si men yeddiiЙ—i. Ko woni, tigi-tigi on, menen men tawiino baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en hiЙ“e gollira nii, meЙ—en Гұentinnde Й“e"."
  26,75,"Ibraahiima maaki: "Enee, on taskike on yi'ii ko wonuЙ—on e rewude gaanin Alla immorde e sanamuuji Й—in"."
  26,76,"Kon ko baabiraaЙ“e mooЙ—on aranЙ“e Й“en laatinoo no rewa."
  26,77,"Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e ayЙ“e am; sabu kamЙ“e ko Й“e meere si wanaa Alla Jooma tageefooji Й—in fow."
  26,78,"On TaguЙ—o lam ko Kanko fewnata lam faade e moЖҙЖҙere aduna e Laakara."
  26,79,"On ko Kanko tun Гұamminta lam si mi weelaama, O yarna lam si mi Й—onЙ—aama."
  26,80,"Si mi nawnii ko Kanko tun woni sellinayЙ—o lam immorde e nawnaare nden, mi alaa sellinoowo ngoo tanaa makko."
  26,81,"E On tawЙ—o ko Kanko tun warata lam si lajal am ngal timmii, O wurnita lam kadi Й“aawo mayde am nden."
  26,82,"Ko Kanko tun mi jortii yawtanay lam goopi am Й—in Г‘alnde njoЙ“di ndin."
  26,83,"Ibraahiima noddi Joomi makko o maaki: Joomam okkam faamugol Diina kan, wattidaa mi e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en immorde e AnnabaaЙ“e adiiЙ“e lam Й“en, Й—um woni naadaa mi ka Aljanna wonndude e maЙ“Й“e"."